A man's penis magically moved to his knees after he slept with a married woman, according to bizarre reports.The man, who has not been named, said his genitals moved position in the blink of an eye.Some believe that the woman's husband put a curse on him after discovering the affair. The Daily Post Kenya reported that the man came out begging for forgiveness after his misdemeanor came to light.In similar reports, a married woman found herself stuck in bed with her lover after another curse was placed on her by the cuckolded husband. The pair, from the town of Kisii, were unable to stand up or move away from each other, and were forced to call for help.